            <title>【CES2025】超輕量寵物追蹤器 GlocalMe GPet    打破定位技術限制</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/glocalme-gpet/life-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=glocalme-gpet</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/glocalme-gpet/life-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Thu, 09 Jan 2025 13:37:26 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[GlocalMe GPet]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286240</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>在 CES 2025 消費科技展，GlocalMe 公司推出全新「GPet」專門為寵物而設，結合雲端 SIM 技術與多重定位方式的定位系統。它體積比上代更為細小，超過 200 個國家和地區都可用到無縫定位服務，用戶在各種環境下均可保持準確追蹤。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286249" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104307-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104307-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104307-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>GlocalMe GPet 結合 GPS、AGPS、LBS、WiFi、藍牙及主動雷達搜尋等六種定位技術，即使在 GPS 和 WiFi 信號不足的密林或室內環境，也可大幅提升定位準確性。雲端 SIM 技術支援全球超過 350 個營運商的多網絡覆蓋，讓基站定位精準度提升超過 50%。</p><p>傳統追蹤裝置在最後 100 米的複雜環境中容易出現失誤，KeyTracker 則透過主動雷達搜尋功能，即使在無 GPS 的情況下，亦能快速找到目標位置，令各種地形追蹤成為可能。</p><h4></h4><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286250" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104314-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104314-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104314-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>這個 GPet 已內置的雲端 SIM 技術免除實體 SIM 卡需求，提供全球連接能力。這款追蹤器針對多種需求，包括個人位置保護、物品追蹤、寵物防走失及全球無縫網絡連接，為日常生活帶來更多便利與安心。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286253" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104320-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104320-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104320-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286256" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104315-694x521.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="521" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104315-694x521.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/img_20250108_104315-scaled.jpg 1200w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/01/09/glocalme-gpet/life-tech/">【CES2025】超輕量寵物追蹤器 GlocalMe GPet    打破定位技術限制</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
