            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1286028</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>ASUS ROG 在 CES 2025 展示了全新升級版的 Flow Z13 (2025)，將遊戲性能與便攜設計結合至極致，配備強勁硬件與突破性設計，為玩家提供頂尖的遊戲體驗。Flow Z13（2025）外觀未作出重大改動，但在提供豐富 I/O 連接埠的基礎上新增專屬 Command Center 控制鍵。硬體方面採用了次世代 AMD Ryzen AI MAX+ 395 處理器。此外螢幕從 3 年前的 FHD 120Hz 升級至 2.5K QHD 180Hz，並引入康寧 Gorilla Glass DXC 技術，進一步提升耐用性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286094" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-scaled.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-1-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><h3><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286031" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_2.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></h3><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286045" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_10.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286042" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_8.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">ROG Flow Z13 2025 可配備最新 AMD Ryzen™ AI MAX+ 395 處理器，具備 16 核心 32 線程，基本時脈達到 3.0GHz，為多工處理與高效能應用提供強大支持。此外 AMD XDNA NPU 提供高達 50TOPS 的 AI 處理能力，進一步提升系統效能。</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286035" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_3.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">ROG Flow Z13 配備 ROG Nebula 霓真技術電競螢幕，尺寸為 13.4 吋，提供 2.5K (2560 x 1600, WQXGA) 解像度與 16:10 長寬比。螢幕採用光面設計，支援 100% DCI-P3 廣色域，具備 180Hz 更新率與 Adaptive-Sync 技術，並通過 Pantone 認證及 Dolby Vision HDR 支援，帶來極致的畫面表現。</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286093" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-scaled.jpg 900w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rogflowz13-144x144.jpg 144w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286041" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_7.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-pm-slice="1 1 []">▲螢幕尺寸為 13.4 吋</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []">ROG Flow Z13 內置 70Wh 大容量電池，支援長時間續航。I/O 連接埠方面，ROG Flow Z13 提供 1 個 3.5mm 音源插孔、1 個 HDMI 2.1 、1 個 USB 3.2 Gen 2 Type-A（數據傳輸速度可達 10Gbps）、2 個 USB 4 Type-C（支援 DisplayPort 和電力傳輸，數據傳輸速度可達 40Gbps），以及 1 個 microSD 卡插槽（UHS-II），充分滿足用戶的連接需求。同時，裝置支援最新的 Wi-Fi 7 技術，讓玩家隨時隨地保持穩定連線。</p><p data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286039" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_6.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-pm-slice="1 1 []"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1286043" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9-580x580.jpg" alt="" width="580" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9-580x580.jpg 580w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9-144x144.jpg 144w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/rog_2025_9.jpg 811w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 580px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;" data-pm-slice="1 1 []">▲鍵盤部分採用背光巧克力鍵盤，支援 1-Zone RGB 燈效</p><h3></h3><p>ASUS 尚未公佈 ROG Flow Z13 的具體上市日期。預計搭載 Ryzen AI Max 390 處理器的版本售價將約為 2,000 美元（約港幣 15,560.28 元），而搭載 Ryzen AI Max+ 395 的版本起價為 2,200 美元（約港幣 17,116.30 元）。</p><p>======</p><p>加入 <a href="https://www.threads.net/@unwirehk" target="_blank" rel="noopener">unwire thread</a> 傾傾科技背後黑暗事</p><p>========</p><br /><b>
